<h1>Work In Progress</h1>
<p>31/01/2014 - This software is in first draft and will not run out of the box</p>
<h2>JSON REST API and CMS Built on NodeJS with a MONGODB datastore</h2>

<hr/>
<h2>Key Components</h2>

<ul>
 <li>DustJS-Linkedin Server side templating for SEO</li>
 <li>MONGODB Query Syntax for the REST API</li>
</ul>

<h2>Concepts</h2>

<ul>
<li>CMS Admin is routed through the REST api for all CRUD operations to allow for update of data from multiple applications</li>
<li>Website can be navigated by the REST API through meaningful HIATUS</li>
<ul>

<h2>Goal</h2>

<ul>
<li>To create website/ecommerce building software that has clear data and presentation separation</li>
</ul>